## Daily Notes Workflow

### Morning
1. Create daily note from template
2. Review yesterday's notes and "tomorrow's priority"
3. Set today's 3 focus items
4. List tasks for work/personal/learning

### End of Day
1. Update task completion status
2. Write reflection (what went well, what to improve)
3. Set tomorrow's top priority

